column5: Wow the leafs have pulled ahead of the Islanders in the goals for department by 1. We are on our way.

...well on the way with games in Washington then Pitts, followed by Philly , wrapping up with PriceN montreal on HNIC.... Wonder what the pro-line is on those games...lol Leafs generally play well against these teams year after year after generation after generation but with this team...Ya stil dont know, I wish them well.
Yah its gonna be another tough week as a leafs fan.
